    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This car is an absolute gem and truly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It is in pristine, mint condition with a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. You won't find a single blemish on this beauty\u2014it's been meticulously maintained and is ready for its next owner to enjoy a perfect driving experience.",
